{
  "name": "ui",
  "version": "0.0.0",
  "description": "User Interface Service",
  "main": "index.js",
  "scripts": {
    "compile": "echo 'No compile needed'",
    "compile-client": "NODE_ENV=production webpack --config ./client/webpack.config.js",

config_files.src/app/UI/Dockerfile:
FROM codefarm/appnodebase:0.0.0

RUN yarn run compile-client -- --env.global_modules_dir ${farmerHome}/.node_modules && \
  rm -rf babel_cache

ENV NODE_ENV production
CMD [ \
    "node", \
    ".", \
    "--bus", "amqp://rabbitmq:5672/codefarm" \
]
